thread.title: MARIA

author: MARIA
title: MARIA
text: I haven't had any issues with the first black cartridge of ink I installed on my computer. I have even lost track of how many pages I have printed, but I'm sure It's more than 200. The ink quality is very good, it doesn't smudge, and it dries up quickly. Had I spent money on the package deal for "ink cartridges" that comes with the HP 7640, i would have already had to get about 5 cartridges, and this one I currently have in the machine is my second one, and it's still going strong.
